effect.frightsdelight.chills.description: You feel a spectral presence nearby, you may feel a chill if they pass through you.
effect.frightsdelight.fortified_mind.des: Removes and grants immunity to Hysteria and Chills.
effect.frightsdelight.hysteria.descripti: Your mind may play tricks on you... Monsters can be hear near and far.
effect.frightsdelight.slimed.description: Slightly decreases walking speed; you may also hear the occasional slimy sound.
effect.frightsdelight.undead_hunger.desc: Removes and grants immunity to Food Poisoning and Infected.
frightsdelight.advancement.craft_best.de: Food in plates, bowls, and drinks seem to be the "safest" to consume
Cooking the food in different ways seems to make the effect less common
frightsdelight.advancement.craft_punch_b: Drinks can be combined and placed. Grab a bottle and have a sip!
frightsdelight.advancement.get_monster_d: Food made with monster drops may not look good ... but some say it tastes like chicken. Beware of adverse effects.
frightsdelight.advancement.get_soul_berr: These can be found in Bastion chests in the Nether and require a Soul Flame source nearby to grow. Berries will shimmer if growing
frightsdelight.advancement.get_wither_be: Soul Berry Bush can be turned into this in the dark with a Wither Essence source very close. Berries will smoke if growing
frightsdelight.advancement.master_chef.d: Conquer all food and drink items in Fright's Delight
frightsdelight.advancement.root.desc: Welcome to a world of unusual delights. Consume with caution.
frightsdelight.effect.chills.chance: You feel like you are being watched ...
frightsdelight.effect.chills.encounter: You feel a chill run down your spine ...
frightsdelight.effect.chills.end: A warmth returns to the air ...
frightsdelight.effect.chills.start: You feel a chill in the air ...
